snippet.title: SYNTAXIA - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST Now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2920940/SYNTAXIA/

Try the DEMO here!
https://spelkollektivet.itch.io/syntaxia

SYNTAXIA is a dream-dark adventure game that allows you to rewrite reality itself by changing the words that describe it. Use your creativity and intuition to escape. Which path will you choose?

#gamedev #horrorgaming #indiegame
